This directory contains a shell agnostic build scripts (*-cmake) meant to build
CISM on the Grizzly HPC system.

To build in this directory you might run the command:
> source grizzly-intel-cmake

followed by 
> make

WARNING: this script was written to be machine compliant at a given time.
If you are experiencing build problem, make sure that the loaded modules are 
up-to-date with what is available on you HPC


